CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 16, 1966, pg. 11B reads: "Promoting Health-O-Rama - The men's committee for the Health-O-Rama at the Savoy Ballroom April 14 through April 17 discuss plans for enrolling the men necessary to control the huge crowds expected. The Health-O-Rama is sponsored by the United Fund's Health Research and Services Foundation."
TitMainTitle: Eight members of United Fund Health-O-Rama men's committee, including Monsignor Paul Bassompierre on left, holding banner in interior
